thread.title: Experts predict 'A Fantastic Woman' will take the Oscar for best Foreign Language film

title: Experts predict 'A Fantastic Woman' will take the Oscar for best Foreign Language film
text:
Experts predict 'A Fantastic Woman' will take the Oscar for best Foreign Language film Saturday, March 03, 2018 - 01:46 
Foreign language Oscar nominees are hosted at A.M.P.A.S., and critics say Chile's 'A Fantastic Woman' is likely to snatch the Oscar. Gavino Garay reports.
